# Trade by SCI / LLM settings
# Configure your AI provider in Settings > AI tab, or set here:
# TRADE_SCI_API_BASE_URL=  (auto-detected from provider)
# TRADE_SCI_API_KEY=       (set in Settings > API Keys)
